tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_privacy_settings (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    birthday DATE,
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE access_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    action VARCHAR(50),
    date_time TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_privacy_settings(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE privacy_settings (
  setting_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  location_privacy BOOLEAN,
  contact_privacy BOOLEAN,
  age_privacy BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  full_name STRING,
  email STRING,
  phone_number STRING,
  date_of_birth DATE
)

CREATE TABLE privacy_settings (
  privacy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT REFERENCES user_profiles(user_id),
  email_privacy BOOLEAN,
  phone_number_privacy BOOLEAN,
  date_of_birth_privacy BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE access_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT REFERENCES user_profiles(user_id),
  access_time TIMESTAMP,
  accessed_data STRING
)

CREATE TABLE login_history (
  login_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT REFERENCES user_profiles(user_id),
  login_time TIMESTAMP,
  login_ip STRING
)

CREATE TABLE user_sessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT REFERENCES user_profiles(user_id),
  session_start_time TIMESTAMP,
  session_end_time TIMESTAMP
)
